Available Tools: get_current_weather | get_feels_like | get_pressure | get_visibility
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "location": "string", "metrics": ["string"] }
Response Schema: { "location": "string", "metrics": { "temperature": number, "humidity": number, "pressure": number } }
---
Question: What are the current temperature, humidity, and pressure in Dubai, UAE?
Call: { "func_call": "get_current_weather", "location": "Dubai, UAE", "metrics": ["temperature", "humidity", "pressure"] }
Response: { "location": "Dubai, UAE", "metrics": { "temperature": 38.4, "humidity": 45, "pressure": 1006.7 } }

Question: I need the weather stats for Bangkok, Thailand including temp, moisture, and air pressure.
Call: { "func_call": "get_current_weather", "location": "Bangkok, Thailand", "metrics": ["temperature", "humidity", "pressure"] }
Response: { "location": "Bangkok, Thailand", "metrics": { "temperature": 33.1, "humidity": 79, "pressure": 1008.3 } }

